  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC422">
  <l>vārā marapiṉa varakkū ṟutalu</l>
	<l>meṉṉā marapiṉa veṉakkū ṟutalu</l>
	<l>maṉṉavai yellā mavaṟṟavaṟ ṟiyalpā</l>
	<l>ṉiṉṉa veṉṉuṅ kuṟippurai yākum.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl tokai yatikāraṅ kūṟiṉāṉ ; avai yellāmviṭṭu, iṉi oru coṉmarapu vaḻūukkāttal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : iyaṅkātavaṟṟai iyaṅkuvatupōlaccollutalum, coṉṉikaḻātavaṟṟaic coṉṉikaḻttuvaṉa pōlac collutalum, avvap poruḷiyalpu paṟṟi avai aṉṉa ceykaiyuṭaiyavaṟṟaippōlac collaluṟṟāṉ ; atu maṉak kuṟippiṉāṉ āyntu, avaṟṟatu urai aṉṟu eṉpatu koḷka.
<p>'aṉṉavai ellām' eṉpatu, avvārāmarapiṉavum palvakaiya, orōvoṉṟēyalla eṉṟaṟku eṉpatu.</p>
<p>vārāmarapiṉa varakkūṟutal varumāṟu :</p>
<p>malai vantu kiṭantatu, neṟi vantu kiṭantatu eṉa varum ; malaikkum neṟikkum aṉṉa ceykai yiṉṟākaliṉ eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṉi, eṉṉāmarapiṉa eṉakkūṟutal varumāṟu :</p>
<p>nilam valleṉṟatu, ilai pacceṉṟatu eṉavum, `ceṅkāṉārāy eṉavum varum.</p>
vilaṅkum maraṉum puḷḷum uḷḷanōy uṟṟāṟkku maṉakkuṟaikku maṟutalaimāṟṟam kūṟuvaṉa pōluṅ kuṟippiṉavākap pulappaṭutalāl itu collappaṭṭatu eṉpatu.	(26)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

